<span itemprop='name'>Video Game Philosopher</span>
</a>
</span>
</span>
<span class='post-timestamp'>
at
<meta content='http://vgtheory.blogspot.com/2014/06/casual-vs-elite-gaming.html' itemprop='url'/>
<a class='timestamp-link' href='http://www.vgtheory.blogspot.com/2014/06/casual-vs-elite-gaming.html' rel='bookmark' title='permanent link'><abbr class='published' itemprop='datePublished' title='2014-06-23T09:35:00-07:00'>9:35 AM</abbr></a>
